Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RRRRRRRYYYEEEEEEEE！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙空间？哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从肺部喷出空气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过产生的气压改变轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去地球！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结…结冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空气结冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦离开人体 就结冰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法改变轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回不去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡兹再也没能回到地球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他变成了介于矿石和生物的中间生命体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在宇宙空间无尽地徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 想死也死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逐渐地 卡兹放弃思考了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:55.35,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(640,590)\be4}纽约郊外 1939年4月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:15:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我们在天上的父
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}愿人尊您之圣名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}愿您的国降临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}愿您的意旨行在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}如同行在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:10.12,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,600)\be4}乔瑟夫·乔斯达（1920年～1939年）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了 JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想来 跟你认识了才半年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我一辈子都不会忘记你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉娜小姐 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要着凉了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再留一会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜猜我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 各位 我好不容易回到纽约
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.30,0:16:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么都没人来接我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后问了一下 你们都到墓地参加葬礼来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我好找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 莉莎莉莎老师 伤好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅西纳也在呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呀 还是想找修特罗哈姆弄个更好使的手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这形势看来要跟德国开战呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疯汉 不知道看看场合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疯汉？你说疯汉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才喊我疯汉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了 走开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}别麻烦到人家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好了 听我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丫的 刚才喊我疯子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 JoJo还活着！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活着？等等 为什么看到我那么吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.93,0:17:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个个都撞鬼似的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神马！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我的名字刻在墓碑上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难…难道这葬礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo 你的伤还没好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要淋雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.47,0:17:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 撑伞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是CJQ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无名指上的戒指是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那么你们也不知道我老婆了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆呀 讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一上来就这样介绍人家…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘎 好害羞 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你个头啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候我被火山连岩石一起冲上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩石刚好成了保护壁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大难不死掉进海里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给威尼斯的渔船救上岸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来的两星期 你在威尼斯照顾我养伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些事情 他们好像都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的有发电报吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电…电报…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错！你答应过的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样嘎达嘎达的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起！我忘记了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OH NO！难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个婆娘的脑子怎么长的！等着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起有用的话还要警察干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo…
