Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,10,,时间继续流淌 世代更替
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撞上了 疼吗 大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是的 都怪你不看着前方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没关系 谁不会犯错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你是日本人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 话就不是这样说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼！
